# Terraform provider cache + state — never commit
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# Per-module lock files are verification artifacts; only the root
# infra/.terraform.lock.hcl is committed to pin provider versions.
modules/*/.terraform.lock.hcl
